data.description:
This spacious and move-in ready home offers 2,052 square feet of living space, making it perfect for those who appreciate room to spread out. With 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, it provides comfortable accommodation for everyone. Additionally, there is a bonus room and an office, adding versatility to the layout.
The highlight of this home is the large and luxurious primary suite, which includes a separate sitting room, office, or nursery – the perfect retreat for relaxation or work. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, complete with a stone fireplace, to the dining area, making it an ideal space for entertaining and gatherings. Convenience is a key feature, with a dedicated laundry/mud room to keep things organized. This property is also situated within a short drive to shopping and restaurants, ensuring that you have easy access to all the amenities you need. It offers the best of both comfort and convenience, making it an ideal place to call home.
